description: Story of my "username".  Some think it's weird or rude. I don't know why!! So here's how I got it.  A few years ago my friend and I were playing a lame trivia game.  We got MOST of questions wrong.  Everytime we got one wrong, a video clip would appear of an ANCIENT prototype plane with wings that actually "flapped" and it would flap across the screen and crash, with the message "FLAPHARDER".  It became our go to word for whenever we do something really stupid or we need to try harder.  Maybe it was one of those things where "you had to be there" to find it funny...but we found it hilarious.  Possibly because it was about 2am at the time.  Anyway, we annoyed all our friends with our "flapharder" mantra for a long time, but we were amused....so who cares??   So please don't think that my username is rude or something that it is not....it's just me "trying harder" to have a fun life :D
